 (不不不)，從來不會。」<br />\n<br />\n「賽會應該好好研究一下他的球鞋，可能加裝了什麼反彈的裝置，這可害我輸了一條波纜，他媽的。」拉斯普金最後抱怨到。<br />\n<br />\nNineup報記者意大利報道"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"不願面對牙朗實力"},{"pid":"f31cf615c07e0c54cef5c09a2225069151ae5f91","tid":1788730,"uid":182792,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:08:01.000Z","msg":"出返nineup報  唔好做五毛分化狗咪幾好"},{"pid":"7bd17f2bbd8b9d99a1994725bce0bcc294b0d81b","tid":1788730,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:12:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b5b14358741d319c71129a4f96f1f8eb16519b","tid":1788730,"uid":96896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"牙朗：開啟飛行模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167a6ec50bbef493e5e0523e1b8123e0a3066c6d","tid":1788730,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4aef5f498a2be17e70955faf10c9ed64a9709f19","tid":1788730,"uid":34419,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"點止4秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係你張圖度數到成10秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6badf6497c7490af663bfc2cf745469aa0e50f","tid":1788730,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744b5720a2728376d370388b3828c0ae06bd4207","tid":1788730,"uid":98813,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3